{"title":"利用 Hexo 建立 GitHub 寄存網誌","uid":"a990d8c2eefbb26d914d318577aa9256","slug":"hexo-create-blog","date":"2022-12-23T23:53:52.000Z","updated":"2022-12-24T00:30:37.975Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo-create-blog.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"利用-Hexo-建立-GitHub-寄存網誌\"><a href=\"#利用-Hexo-建立-GitHub-寄存網誌\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"利用 Hexo 建立 GitHub 寄存網誌\"></a>利用 Hexo 建立 GitHub 寄存網誌</h1><p>大家好，歡迎來到我的網誌。欸。。？這裏為什麼好像。。整個樣子都不一樣啊。。</p>\n<p>對啦，因為我「搬家」了。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"棄暗投明轉用-Hexo\"><a href=\"#棄暗投明轉用-Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"棄暗投明轉用 Hexo\"></a>棄暗投明轉用 Hexo</h1><p>為什麼我要由 Google Blogspot 轉用 Hexo？因為 Blogspot 在加載網誌實在太慢了！！！！有時還要跑不起來。。。於是就改用 Hexo 建立網誌了，安裝方法不複雜，現在開始。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"什麼是-Hexo？\"><a href=\"#什麼是-Hexo？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"什麼是 Hexo？\"></a>什麼是 Hexo？</h1><p>Hexo 是一個快速、簡單且強大的網誌框架。Hexo 使用 Markdown（或其他標記語言）解析您的文章，並在幾秒鐘內，透過漂亮的主題產生靜態檔案。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">WARNING</p>\n<p>我用的是 Mac OS，Windows 用戶可參考官方文案（但其實與 Mac OS 的差不多，可作以下內容參考）。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">WARNING</p>\n<p>以下我的安裝教學是使用 Homebrew，請預必先安裝 Homebrew 以繼續接下來的教學，請到 <a href='https://brew.sh/' target='_blank'>官方網站</a> 瞭解安裝 Homebrew。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"安裝-Git\"><a href=\"#安裝-Git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 Git\"></a>安裝 Git</h1><p>在終端機輸入：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew install git\nbrew install git-gui</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"安裝-Nodejs\"><a href=\"#安裝-Nodejs\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 Nodejs\"></a>安裝 Nodejs</h1><p>可到官方下載 Nodejs 軟件包，<a href=\"http://nodejs.org/\" target=\"_blank\">按此下載</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"安裝-Hexo\"><a href=\"#安裝-Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 Hexo\"></a>安裝 Hexo</h1><p>如果以上的都安裝好了，便可以在終端機執行：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install -g hexo-cli</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"解決-EACCES-權限問題\"><a href=\"#解決-EACCES-權限問題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解決 EACCES 權限問題\"></a>解決 EACCES 權限問題</h2><p>不過，如果在嘗試安裝 Hexo 的過程中出現 EACCES 權限錯誤，請遵循由 npmjs 發布的指導修復該問題。官方強烈建議不要使用 <code>root</code>、<code>sudo</code> 等方法覆蓋權限。</p>\n<p>這裏有簡單的解決方法：在終端機輸入。</p>\n<p>首先，先在根目錄裏建立新資料夾 npm-global。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mkdir ~&#x2F;.npm-global</code></pre>\n\n<p>然後把新資料夾 npm-global 設定為 npm 預設路徑。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">NPM_CONFIG_PREFIX&#x3D;~&#x2F;.npm-global</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p>詳情可見 <a href=\"https://docs.npmjs.com/resolving-eacces-permissions-errors-when-installing-packages-globally\" target=\"_blank\">npmjs 指導</a> 。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"安裝-VSCode-Hexo-擴充套件\"><a href=\"#安裝-VSCode-Hexo-擴充套件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 VSCode Hexo 擴充套件\"></a>安裝 VSCode Hexo 擴充套件</h1><p>雖然官方比較建議 Mac OS 用戶使用 XCode，但我堅決不把它下載下來，因為。。它有 7.8GB 之多啊。。。（其實我下載過，不過後來把它刪除了）。</p>\n<p>而我是較常用 VSCode 的，所以就推薦大家用 VSCode，何況 VSCode 有 Hexo 擴充套件，何樂而不為呢？</p>\n<p>到 VSCode 擴充套件庫下載 <code>vscode-hexo</code>，或 <a href=\"vscode:extension/codeyu.vscode-hexo\">按此下載</a>。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"基本指令\"><a href=\"#基本指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本指令\"></a>基本指令</h1><p>對於 Mac OS 用戶，進行使用 <code>hexo</code> 指令前，需要輸入 <code>npx</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p>參考資料：<a href='https://medium.com/itsems-frontend/whats-npx-e83400efe7f8' target='_blank'>Medium</a></p>\n<p>Npm (node package manger) 是套件管理工具，讓你在開發過程中，可以把想要的 <code>node</code> 套件，透過 <code>npm</code> 安裝在 <code>local</code> 專案位置或是 <code>global</code> 全局性整台電腦的環境下面。</p>\n<p>我只是想要測試一下這個套件是不是我要的，可是我一定要把他安裝下來<br>這就是 <code>npx</code> 用處所在了。</p>\n<p><code>npx</code> 是在 npm v5.2.0 之後內建的指令，也是一種 CLI 工具，讓我們可以更方便的安裝或是管理依賴 (dependencies)，就來看看 <code>npx</code> 可以怎麼幫助我們，以及和 <code>npm</code> 主要的差異在哪裡。\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"初始化網誌\"><a href=\"#初始化網誌\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化網誌\"></a>初始化網誌</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo init [資料夾名稱]</code></pre>\n<p>例如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo init hexo</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"新增文章\"><a href=\"#新增文章\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新增文章\"></a>新增文章</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo new [文章名稱]</code></pre>\n\n<p>例如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo new &quot;HelloWorld&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">WARNING</p>\n<p>文章名稱是將會應用並命名到檔案名稱，所以請以英文為主，慎防和遲免程式因亂碼出錯，還有不需要加上副檔名，因為會自動以 <code>.md</code> 格式生成，例如 <code>HelloWorld.md</code>。</p>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">---\ntitle: 文章標題\ndate: 2022-12-24 00:13:26\n---\n\n文章內容由此處開始</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"發佈文章\"><a href=\"#發佈文章\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"發佈文章\"></a>發佈文章</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo deploy</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p><code>deploy</code> 是部署。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"本機預覽\"><a href=\"#本機預覽\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本機預覽\"></a>本機預覽</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo server</code></pre>\n\n<p>這樣你便可以經 <code>localhost:4000</code> 本機伺服器看看預覽結果。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"部署到-GitHub\"><a href=\"#部署到-GitHub\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署到 GitHub\"></a>部署到 GitHub</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"建立-Repository\"><a href=\"#建立-Repository\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建立 Repository\"></a>建立 Repository</h2><p>進入 <a href=\"https://github.com\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a> 網頁，點擊 <code>New</code> 按鈕新建專案，把 <code>Repository name</code> 命名為 <code>username.github.io</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p><code>username</code> 是你的用戶名稱。</p>\n</div>\n<p>然後按 <code>Create repository</code>。那就成功建立網域 <code>username.github.io</code>。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"把檔案推送到-GitHub\"><a href=\"#把檔案推送到-GitHub\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"把檔案推送到 GitHub\"></a>把檔案推送到 GitHub</h2><hr>\n<h3 id=\"安裝-Git-相關套件\"><a href=\"#安裝-Git-相關套件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 Git 相關套件\"></a>安裝 Git 相關套件</h3><p>回到 <code>hexo</code> 資料夾，在終端機輸入：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"修改-config-yml-檔案的-deploy-設定\"><a href=\"#修改-config-yml-檔案的-deploy-設定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改 _config.yml 檔案的 deploy 設定\"></a>修改 _config.yml 檔案的 deploy 設定</h2><div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">WARNING</p>\n<p>這個 <code>_config.yml</code> 是 <code>hexo</code> 根目錄內，並非 <code>hexo/themes/</code> 內那個。</p>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">deploy:\n    type: git\n    repo: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;username&#x2F;username.github.io.git\n    branch: master</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p><code>type</code>：選擇部屬模式，這裡填 <code>git</code><br><code>repo</code>：GitHub repository 的連結，記得將 <code>username</code> 修改成自己的帳號名稱<br><code>branch</code>：選擇分支，預設為 <code>master</code></p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"部署\"><a href=\"#部署\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署\"></a>部署</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">hexo deploy</code></pre>\n\n<p>在每次進行修改後，通常都會做以下三部曲，避免更新不完全。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p><code>cl</code> 是 <code>clean</code>，清除快取檔案 <code>db.json</code> 和 <code>public</code> 已產生靜態檔案。<br><code>g</code> 是 <code>generate</code>，產生靜態檔案。<br><code>d</code> 是 <code>deploy</code>，部署網站。</p>\n</div>\n<p>那就可以到 <code>https://username.github.io</code> 造訪網誌了。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>好了教學到這了，希望大家學會 Hexo 建立網誌，有問題歡迎在下面留言，下篇文章再見。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"利用 Hexo 建立 GitHub 寄存網誌大家好，歡迎來到我的網誌。欸。。？這裏為什麼好像。。整個樣子都不一樣啊。。 對啦，因為我「搬家」了。 棄暗投明轉用 Hexo為什麼我要由 Google Blogspot 轉用 Hexo？因為 Blogspot 在加載網誌實在太慢了！！！...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.6k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"網頁開發","slug":"網頁開發","count":1,"path":"api/categories/網頁開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"終端機指令","slug":"終端機指令","count":1,"path":"api/tags/終端機指令.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8-Hexo-%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B-GitHub-%E5%AF%84%E5%AD%98%E7%B6%B2%E8%AA%8C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">利用 Hexo 建立 GitHub 寄存網誌</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A3%84%E6%9A%97%E6%8A%95%E6%98%8E%E8%BD%89%E7%94%A8-Hexo\"><span class=\"toc-text\">棄暗投明轉用 Hexo</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF-Hexo%EF%BC%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">什麼是 Hexo？</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D-Git\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安裝 Git</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D-Nodejs\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安裝 Nodejs</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D-Hexo\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安裝 Hexo</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA-EACCES-%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%90%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">解決 EACCES 權限問題</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D-VSCode-Hexo-%E6%93%B4%E5%85%85%E5%A5%97%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安裝 VSCode Hexo 擴充套件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基本指令</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E7%B6%B2%E8%AA%8C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">初始化網誌</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">新增文章</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">發佈文章</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9C%AC%E6%A9%9F%E9%A0%90%E8%A6%BD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">本機預覽</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%88%B0-GitHub\"><span class=\"toc-text\">部署到 GitHub</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B-Repository\"><span class=\"toc-text\">建立 Repository</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8A%8A%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81%E5%88%B0-GitHub\"><span class=\"toc-text\">把檔案推送到 GitHub</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D-Git-%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E5%A5%97%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安裝 Git 相關套件</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9-config-yml-%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84-deploy-%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">修改 _config.yml 檔案的 deploy 設定</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">部署</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"ma